text.text: Temple as per faith of North Indian Hindus. Most of the festivals are celebrated here. Every Saturday and Tuesday, Sudarkand is read here at 7PM.

originalText.text: Temple as per faith of North Indian Hindus. Most of the festivals are celebrated here. Every Saturday and Tuesday, Sudarkand is read here at 7PM.

text.text: Love the temple vibes. All Hindu festivals are celebrated with full enthusiasm. We await festival time and the celebration at temple. I got to know about importance of few festivals after I started attending their celebrations. The feel of Prasad and bhandaara is the next level. You feel like you are in India. Though all the people are strangers in temple but still you come out knowing some or the other person. The mood uplifts immediately after visiting the temple.
